text: The Will is a newspaper from Nigeria that comes out every week. Austyn Ogannah started it in 2009 in a place called San Francisco in America. Later, it started working in Nigeria too. The newspaper writes about different things that are important to people in Nigeria like news, politics, business, art, sports, and other important events. The Will is made by The Will News Media. == References == Category:Newspapers published in Nigeria
title: The Will (newspaper)
